    </h3>
    <li parent="kix.waqkeam4gc8x">
      <t>Led design and development of ExtraSuite, an open-source CLI framework enabling AI agents (Claude Code, Codex) to securely operate on Google Workspace files</t>
    </li>
    <li parent="kix.waqkeam4gc8x">
      <t>Implemented a pull/diff/push reconciliation engine in Python that converts Google Docs API JSON into editable XML and back — handling rich formatting, tables, lists, headers, footers, footnotes, and nested styles</t>
